{"tid":1502226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本名作家河添恵子824拍片支持示威者：如果我係香港人  都會以死相搏","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:15:24.000Z","uid":221265,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"46f17f7bc9ca6e39760bb21b839327f990dc9814","tid":1502226,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFXkBzvBYuA&amp;t=99s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmFXkBzvBYuA%26t%3D99s&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84oD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=80d67b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mFXkBzvBYuA&amp;t=99s</a><br />\n<br />\n河添恵子(後生幾靚女)<br />\n上個月出嘅書『米中新冷戦の正体 - 脱中国で日本再生』<a href=\"http://喺amazon.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%96%BAamazon.jp&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84oD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=2da6f2c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">喺amazon.jp</a>中國研究類仲係第一位，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBqe7nY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBqe7nY.jpg&h=d4eadadd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2c5uBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2c5uBo.jpg&h=af458b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mraFH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mraFH1.jpg&h=ff436684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zo47HXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZo47HXB.jpg&h=b02098fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇佢講香港，佢都跟得好貼，例：5:53<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果我係香港人，得香港特區護照，我都會以死相搏</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50ayDvk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50ayDvk.jpg&h=d2439e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGRNHWO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGRNHWO.jpg&h=7514eed0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今年56歲嘅佢，話80年代中，嚟過幾次香港，當時住喺啲平價guesthouse, 同咗guesthouse<br />\n東主fd咗，當年東主2公婆365日都好勤力做嘢，只食啲100幾yen一餐嘅飯盒，為嘅就係喺97前逃離香港，儲$移民。到90年代頭，2夫婦終於拿到外國居留權。 <br />\n<br />\n河添恵子話當年嘅香港人，都為下一代努力移民，今次反送中事件，佢眼見好多都係無力移民，只有香港特區護照嘅香港人，同埋除咗後生仔，仲係誇世代嘅，佢覺得香港人好可憐，話日本人從來覺得自由同民主都係好似空氣中嘅存在，唔駛$理所當然有嘅嘢，但香港人唔係咁諗，依20幾年來，越來越感覺到正在失去。 佢同時理解抗爭者點解會越來越升級暴力。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVtMd3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVtMd3q.jpg&h=b03dd677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢仲呼籲日本有能之士都要努力支持香港人！佢話華人都以有樓為大，無樓結唔到婚，生唔到仔，只係弱者，依家越來越多人住喺啲又細又殘又遠嘅樓/劏房，感到絕望。 <br />\n<br />\n片尾佢仲整咗啲slogan 用中日英文寫：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRHdDuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRHdDuV.jpg&h=c157c965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油！世解將會改變<br />\n頑張ろう香港！世界は変わる！<br />\nLet's do our best Hong Kong, The world would change!</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BFnwQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BFnwQw.jpg&h=b463c989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b029b49e2f181f6d15201cabe6f51b7fe7280228","tid":1502226,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e85f7eb09d0fb8d000891335f021385167f7fc7a","tid":1502226,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"習敗北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c826e889ae83a4db8174e63586ed5c405705ab3","tid":1502226,"uid":49208,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:26:43.000Z","msg"